      image(images.at("figure-20-11").path, width: 80%),
      caption: images.at("figure-20-11").caption
    )

    #figure(
      image(images.at("figure-20-12").path, width: 80%),
      caption: images.at("figure-20-12").caption
    )

8.  **Feeding**:
    -   **Gastric Mill**: Two-part stomach with calcareous teeth for grinding.

